<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Daniel's SkyAdvantures 作品集</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;700;800&family=Long+Cang&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background-color: #0e0e1a;
      background-image:
        radial-gradient(white, rgba(255,255,255,.2) 2px, transparent 40px),
        radial-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.4), rgba(255,255,255,.15) 1px, transparent 30px),
        radial-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.5), rgba(255,255,255,.1) 2px, transparent 20px),
        radial-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.2), rgba(255,255,255,.05) 1px, transparent 10px);
      background-size:
        500px 500px,
        300px 300px,
        200px 200px,
        100px 100px;
      animation: move-stars 150s linear infinite;
    }
    @keyframes move-stars {
      from { background-position:0 0,50px 50px,250px 250px,150px 150px; }
      to { background-position:500px 500px,350px 350px,450px 450px,250px 250px; }
    }
    .drone-body { animation: float-up 8s ease-in-out infinite; }
    .drone-controller { animation: float-down 8s ease-in-out infinite; animation-delay:1s; }
    @keyframes float-up {0%{transform:translateY(0) rotate(-3deg);}50%{transform:translateY(-20px) rotate(3deg);}100%{transform:translateY(0) rotate(-3deg);} }
    @keyframes float-down {0%{transform:translateY(0) rotate(3deg);}50%{transform:translateY(20px) rotate(-3deg);}100%{transform:translateY(0) rotate(3deg);} }
    @media (max-width:768px){.drone-bg-images{display:none}}
  </style>
</head>

<body class="dark bg-slate-100 text-slate-800 antialiased">
<div id="app" class="min-h-screen flex flex-col">

  <header class="border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800">
    <nav class="container mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400">Daniel's SkyAdvantures</h1>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main class="flex-grow">

    <section id="landing-view" class="h-screen min-h-[700px] flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center p-6 relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="drone-bg-images absolute inset-0 z-0">

        <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/QHCRV7x4/20251017-043255078-i-OS.avif"
             alt="Potensic Atom 2 Drone Body"
             class="drone-body absolute top-[15%] left-[5%] md:left-[15%] w-1/3 max-w-[250px] lg:max-w-sm rounded-lg shadow-2xl opacity-80">

        <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/XXQRVL3Z/IMG-0798.jpg"
             alt="Potensic Atom 2 Controller"
             class="drone-controller absolute bottom-[15%] right-[5%] md:right-[15%] w-1/4 max-w-[200px] lg:max-w-xs rounded-lg shadow-2xl opacity-80">

        <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/Nj5954Yc/drone-battery-hub.jpg"
             alt="Potensic Atom 2 Battery Charging Hub"
             class="drone-body absolute top-[60%] left-[5%] w-1/5 max-w-[150px] lg:max-w-xs rounded-lg shadow-2xl opacity-70"
             style="animation-delay: 2s; animation-duration: 7s;">

        <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/3RxBqP3b/propeller-set.jpg"
             alt="Replacement Propeller Set"
             class="drone-controller absolute top-[10%] right-[10%] w-1/6 max-w-[100px] lg:max-w-[150px] rounded-lg shadow-2xl opacity-75"
             style="animation-delay: 3s; animation-duration: 9s;">
      </div>

      <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold mb-4 text-white" style="text-shadow:2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);">Daniel's SkyAdvantures</h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">透過 Potensic Atom 2 的鏡頭探索世界</p>
        <a href="#gallery-view" class="inline-block bg-blue-700 dark:bg-blue-400 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full text-lg hover:bg-blue-800 dark:hover:bg-blue-500 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg">
          探索作品集
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div id="gallery-view" class="container mx-auto px-6 py-8 md:py-12">
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-4xl mb-4">攝影日誌</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-300">每一次起飛，都是一次重新看見世界的方式。</p>
      </div>

      <div id="video-grid" class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

        <div class="video-card rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
          <img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/8Y8v-Ke__UQ/hqdefault.jpg" alt="城市夜幕光軌" class="w-full h-48 object-cover">
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">城市夜幕光軌</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 text-sm">在台北市高空俯瞰車流與都市燈海，夜色中車輛的尾燈化為光軌，如流星滑過城市的靜夜。</p>
            <div class="mt-4 aspect-w-16 aspect-h-9">
              <iframe class="w-full h-full rounded-lg"
                      src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/8Y8v-Ke__UQ"
                      title="城市夜幕光軌" frameborder="0"
                      allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
                      allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="video-card rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
          <img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/ZBcUvJxt3n8/hqdefault.jpg" alt="陽明山日間風光" class="w-full h-48 object-cover">
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">陽明山日間風光</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 text-sm">翱翔於陽明山上空，捕捉雲霧在山嶺間流動、陽光穿透林梢的瞬間，感受大自然的脈動與廣闊。</p>
            <div class="mt-4 aspect-w-16 aspect-h-9">
              <iframe class="w-full h-full rounded-lg"
                      src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZBcUvJxt3n8"
                      title="陽明山日間風光" frameborder="0"
                      allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
                      allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="video-card rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
          <img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/rccn0Y0qryc/hqdefault.jpg" alt="基隆港夜景" class="w-full h-48 object-cover">
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">基隆港夜景</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 text-sm">夜幕下的基隆港，船舶燈火與城市光影交織，從空中視角展現港口與海面的倒影如鏡。</p>
            <div class="mt-4 aspect-w-16 aspect-h-9">
              <iframe class="w-full h-full rounded-lg"
                      src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/rccn0Y0qryc"
                      title="基隆港夜景" frameborder="0"
                      allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
                      allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="video-card rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
          <img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/DseaZgo8JAc/hqdefault.jpg" alt="東北角海岸日出" class="w-full h-48 object-cover">
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">東北角海岸日出</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 text-sm">清晨飛行於東北角海岸線，第一道曙光從海平面升起，金色光束灑落在岩岸與海浪之上。</p>
            <div class="mt-4 aspect-w-16 aspect-h-9">
              <iframe class="w-full h-full rounded-lg"
                      src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/DseaZgo8JAc"
                      title="東北角海岸日出" frameborder="0"
                      allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
                      allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="video-card rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
          <img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/35XeMkVmABc/hqdefault.jpg" alt="信義區夜間縮時" class="w-full h-48 object-cover">
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">信義區夜間縮時</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 text-sm">在台北信義區高處，以縮時攝影記錄車流、霓虹與人流交錯的城市節奏，展現不夜城的蓬勃生命。</p>
            <div class="mt-4 aspect-w-16 aspect-h-9">
              <iframe class="w-full h-full rounded-lg"
                      src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/35XeMkVmABc"
                      title="信義區夜間縮時" frameborder="0"
                      allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
                      allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

  </main>

  <footer class="border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-4 text-center text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">
      <p>&copy; 2024 Daniel's SkyAdvantures. 版權所有.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

</div>
</body>
</html>
